{"tid":970359,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片] 中國男子過馬路停低玩電話被撞","createTime":"2019-01-05T17:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T09:35:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96a43ed9112acecbbc6b6a0258fcadbe6c887011","tid":970359,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T17:53:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S1_sfCNP7nk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS1_sfCNP7nk&d=Ut2lqreapOZggIW7OahDSjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=1b8e76bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S1_sfCNP7nk</a><br />\n<br />\n馬路如虎口，出門在外要注意安全，遵守交通規則，否則一不注意，就會讓自己受傷。中國大陸一名男子日前就邊走邊玩手機，還試圖闖馬路，最後慘被車子撞飛。<br />\n<br />\n網友「末日生存守則」在微博貼出這則車禍影片，影片中可以看到，一名男子走在大馬路上，疑似要過馬路，但他沒走斑馬線，也沒看交通號誌，還邊走邊使用手機，路上駕駛看到他後，紛紛繞道而行，但他最後還是被一輛黑色轎車撞上。<br />\n<br />\n原PO指出，男子站在馬路間玩手機被撞飛後，「這樣的車禍誰該全責？」影片曝光後，大部分網友力挺駕駛，認為是男子的錯，還有人指出，「車禍盡量避免脖子轉」，否則必死無疑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=480529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D480529&d=Ut2lqreapOZggIW7OahDSjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=015f01c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D480529&h=7281e708\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=480529</a>"},{"pid":"d754cc81a159d71df25fcf21199e067aba6c5a73","tid":970359,"uid":9328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T18:10:35.000Z","msg":"撞死你又點，賠幾萬蚊搞掂"},{"pid":"4fd63c2f440e4311b2981a97c62e634f1b4f6fcf","tid":970359,"uid":81518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T18:27:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81341f79063294c603ad440555db113508702d7f","tid":970359,"uid":81518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T09:26:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"169649959b676b5d67c03619424786049b17e850","tid":970359,"uid":